              {
                "input": "prompt",
                "title": "User prompt",
                "type": "string",
                "value": "Extrae los datos del informe mensual de rentabilidad de MyInvestor a partir del correo adjunto.\n\n- Ganancias del mes: importe del bloque 'GANANCIAS ... En [mes]' (la ganancia del mes indicado).\n- Aportaciones del mes: aportaciones netas del mes.\n- Valor de la cartera: valor total actual de la cartera.\n- Fecha reporte: ultimo dia natural del mes al que corresponde el informe (indicado en el asunto o cuerpo), en formato AAAA-MM-DD.\n- Titulo: 'MyInvestor AAAA-MM' usando el ano y mes del informe.\n\nLos importes son numeros: elimina simbolos de moneda y separadores de miles y usa punto decimal."
              },
              {
                "input": "codeSandbox",
                "description": "Recommendation: OFF, The task involves understanding and extracting specific information from an email document, which is a comprehension task rather than data transformation or processing. The model should parse the content directly without needing file manipulation in a sandbox environment.",
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "AUTO",
                  "OFF",
                  "ON"
                ],
                "value": "AUTO"
              },
              {
                "input": "webAccess",
                "description": "Recommendation: OFF, The task is to extract data from an attached email/report about MyInvestor profitability. No web access is needed since the data source (email) is already provided by the user.",
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "AUTO",
                  "OFF",
                  "ON"
                ],
                "value": "AUTO"
              },
              {
                "input": "review",
                "title": "Review (human-in-the-loop)",
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
